<codeline><highlight class="normal">/**</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*<sp/>@brief<sp/>Formats<sp/>a<sp/>vector<sp/>of<sp/>tensors<sp/>to<sp/>have<sp/>the<sp/>specified<sp/>dimensions<sp/>and<sp/>concatenates<sp/>them.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*<sp/>@param<sp/>v<sp/>A<sp/>vector<sp/>of<sp/>tensors.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*<sp/>@param<sp/>dim<sp/>The<sp/>desired<sp/>dimensions.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*<sp/>@return<sp/>A<sp/>concatenated<sp/>tensor<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>specified<sp/>dimensions.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>*/</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>format(std::vector&lt;torch::Tensor&gt;<sp/>v,<sp/>std::vector&lt;signed<sp/>long&gt;<sp/>dim){</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::vector&lt;torch::Tensor&gt;<sp/>out;<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>for<sp/>(size_t<sp/>x(0);<sp/>x<sp/>&lt;<sp/>v.size();<sp/>++x){out.push_back(v[x].view(dim));}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>return<sp/>torch::cat(out,<sp/>-1);<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
